Title: Bloodlines
Plot: A casino employee is beaten and raped on her way home from work, but she survives and identifies her attacker. When a DNA test sets him free, Grissom wrestles with his belief that  evidence can ever lie.
GuestStars: Tom Kiesche, Nina Siemaszko, George Newbern, Drew Pillsbury, Michael Reilly Burke, Mark Kiely, Lisa Sheridan, Davenia McFadden, Drew Powell, Lamont D. Thompson, Ty Upshaw, Rachel Winfree, Edmund Wyson
